		<main class="container">
			
		<h2>Inputs for identifying the pre and post condition of a breach</h2>

		<p>To generate the event-state model we need to identify the pre-condition and post-condition of a breach.</p>

		<ol>
		  <li>Find the breach: Using existing auditing and monitoring tools first find the security policy breach</li>
		  <li>Identify the pre-condition of a breach</li>
			<ol>
			  <li>Go to https://fight.mitre.org/ or https://attack.mitre.org/ website</li>
			  <li>Identify the tactics and techniques related to the breach (you can use the search button in the website also)</li>
			  <li>Rank them and select the most appropriate one</li>
			  <li>Additionally, search in the https://d3fend.mitre.org/ website to find out the specific defense mechanism and then check for relevant techniques listed there</li>
			</ol>
		  <li>Identify the post-condition of the breach</li>
			<ol>
			  <li>Using the description of the specific techniques and sub techniques, especially the procedure examples one can find the post condition of the breach</li>
			</ol>
		</ol> 

		<form action="#">
		  <label for="controls"><b>Choose a breached security control:</b></label>
		  <select id="controls" name="controls" >
			<option value="cntrl_1">AC-7: Unsuccessful Logon Attempts</option>
			<option value="cntrl_2">CM-7: Least Functionality</option>
			<option value="cntrl_3">SI-4(2, 7): System Monitoring | Automated Tools and Mechanisms for Real-time Analysis </option>
		  </select><br><br>
		  
		  <label for="fname" title="This is a two to five words title in the format of controlId_CauseOfBreach"><b>Pre-Condition Title:</b></label><br>
		  <p >This is a two to five words title in the format of "controlId_CauseOfBreach"</p>
		  <input type="text" ><br><br>
		  <label for="fname"><b>Pre-Condition Description:</b></label><br>
		  <p>Describe the logic for selecting this pre-condition of the breached security control within 250 words</p>
		  <textarea   id="fname" name="fname" cols="50" rows="10"  maxlength="250"> </textarea><br>

		  <label for="fname" title="This is a two to five words title in the format of controlId_EffectsOfBreach"><b>Post-Condition Title:</b></label><br>
		  <p title="Hello world">This is a two to five words title in the format of "controlId_EffectsOfBreach"</p>
		  <input type="text" ><br><br>
		  <label for="lname"><b>Post-Condition Description:</b></label> <br>
		  <p>Describe the logic for selecting this post-condition of the breached security control within 250 words</p>
		  <textarea   id="lname" name="lname" cols="50" rows="10"  maxlength="250"> </textarea><br><br>


		  <input type="Submit" value="Generate the event-state model">
		</form>
		
		
